sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Kueue Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Cache as Kueue Cache/Queue<br/>(in-process)
    participant Scheduler as Kueue Scheduler<br/>(in-process loop)
    participant JobCtrl as Kueue Job Controller<br/>(in-process)
    participant RemoteAPI as Remote Cluster API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant CloudAPI as Cloud Provider API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,JobCtrl: Flow 1: Job Admission

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Job (suspended=true)<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-batch-v1-job<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS internal certs
    Webhook->>Webhook: Set managedBy label<br/>Validate queue-name
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Job spec
    K8sAPI-->>User: Job created (suspended)

    Note over Cache,Scheduler: Async reconciliation

    K8sAPI->>JobCtrl: Watch event: Job created
    JobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Workload CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Cache: Watch event: Workload created
    Cache->>Cache: Update cluster queue state

    Scheduler->>Cache: Take snapshot
    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Evaluate pending workloads<br/>Check quotas, priorities, flavors
    Scheduler->>K8sAPI: Admit Workload<br/>(set admission status)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>JobCtrl: Watch event: Workload admitted
    JobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Unsuspend Job<br/>(set suspended=false)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>User: Job running

    Note over K8sAPI,RemoteAPI: Flow 2: MultiKueue Federation (optional)

    K8sAPI->>JobCtrl: Watch: Workload with MultiKueue check
    JobCtrl->>RemoteAPI: Create remote Workload<br/>Auth: Kubeconfig credentials
    RemoteAPI-->>JobCtrl: Remote admission status
    JobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Sync status to local Workload<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over K8sAPI,CloudAPI: Flow 3: Provisioning Request (optional)

    K8sAPI->>JobCtrl: Workload needs ProvisioningRequest
    JobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ProvisioningRequest CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>CloudAPI: Cluster autoscaler provisions nodes<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
    CloudAPI-->>K8sAPI: Nodes provisioned
    K8sAPI->>JobCtrl: ProvisioningRequest fulfilled
    JobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update AdmissionCheck → Ready<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
